         <div class="col-sm-6 content">
		 <hr class="top visible-xs">	
            <div class=''><div ><p class="lead">Geldards is committed to ensuring a consistently discrimination free workplace, promoting equality and diversity.</p>

<p>This means that we make sure our employment practices are fair, flexible and enabling so each member of staff can reach their full potential.</p>

<p>Promoting a culture which supports equal opportunities and diversity is not just about responding to legislation or regulation. By working towards the elimination of prejudice and discrimination, Geldards is able to ensure it provides a first class service to our clients and our staff feel valued. </p>

<p>Furthermore, ensuring we attract, develop and retain the best people with diverse characteristics is vital to our firm’s continued success.</p><p>You can view Geldards' latest diversity report by <strong><a href="/Userfiles/documents/Diversity.pdf">clicking here.</a>&nbsp;</strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 19.2px;"></span></p><p>You can view Geldards' Gender Pay Gap Report 2018 by <strong><a href="https://www.geldards.com/UserFiles/documents/Geldards%20Gender%20Pay%20Gap%20Report%202018.pdf">clicking here.</a>&nbsp;</strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 19.2px;"></span></p></div></div><div class=''><div ><div id="placeholderMain_baseExpertise_1_3_control_1_divChart" style="width:auto;height:auto;"></div>
